Introduction

In this homework, its expected to pick 3 different categories of data from Central Bank of the Republic of Turkey(from EVDS System). Also, building three different models from these data sets for one main goal is required.

Main goal of the research is understanding Are economic growth of Trkiye is increasing according to production capacity utilization, empty trucks enter to Trkiye and total workforce. For that we use these independent data given below:

Empty truck entry to Trkiye(TP.UNDNAKLIYE.TBG.TOPLAM.ADET): Export products needs to taken by trucks from Trkiye. In other words, some trucks has no loads should come to Trkiye to load the export products of Trkiye to deliver other countries. During the report, it will be mentioned as truck

Industry capacity utilization of Trkiye(TP.TP.KKO.MA): It includes how much percent of the capacity of the industries used given month category. Amount of export defined how much product produced in other word how the industry is productive to supply exports.During the report, it will be mentioned as productivity

Workforce(TP.TIG03): It defines how many people employed. Amount of workforce might be effective to define production capacity of the industry. On the other hand it shows growth of the Trkiye ecomony along people

Predictor variables data TP.TSANAYMT2021.Y1: Industry production index. It will be used for productivity and truck. Productivity and Truck has some kind of relationship even though it is not strong. If product is produced it also will be transferred. Because of that production index related to two of them. TP.KTF17: Rate of commercial credit. It is especially for productivity because lower rate may cause more investment on productivity. TP.AC2.TOP.A: How many company opened TP.KAP2.TOP.A: How many company closed. Closed and opened company number defines how many people employed so they are key predictor for workforce TP.DK.USD.A.YTL: Turkish lira American Dollar currency. It will be used for truck since it effects its costs.
